# FANMOD Installation Guide  
### RTX 2080 ASUS OC Edition

Welcome to the step-by-step installation tutorial for setting up the FANMOD on the ASUS RTX 2080 OC Edition graphics card. This guide will walk you through each stage of the process with images and brief descriptions to ensure a smooth installation.

---

## Step-by-Step Instructions

### Step 1: Preparation  
![Step 1](tutorials/rtx2080/step1.png)  
Power down your PC and carefully remove the graphics card. Work on a static-free surface.

---

### Step 2: Remove Existing Shroud  
![Step 2](tutorials/rtx2080/step2.png)  
Unscrew and detach the stock cooler or shroud from the GPU without damaging components.

---

### Step 3: Clean the Surface  
![Step 3](tutorials/rtx2080/step3.png)  
Use isopropyl alcohol to clean off thermal paste and any debris.

---

### Step 4: Align FANMOD Brackets  
![Step 4](tutorials/rtx2080/step4.png)  
Align FANMOD mounting brackets with the existing screw holes on your GPU.

---

### Step 5: Attach Cooling Fans  
![Step 5](tutorials/rtx2080/step5.png)  
Secure the 120MM fans to the bracket, ensuring correct orientation and airflow direction.

---

### Step 6: Connect RGB Header  
![Step 6](tutorials/rtx2080/step6.png)  
Connect the RGB cable to your motherboard’s RGB header or controller.

---

### Step 7: Apply Thermal Paste  
![Step 7](tutorials/rtx2080/step7.png)  
Apply new thermal paste to the GPU die and place thermal pads on VRMs if needed.

---

### Step 8: Reinstall the GPU  
![Step 8](tutorials/rtx2080/step8.png)  
Insert the GPU back into the PCIe slot and reconnect power cables.

---

### Step 9: Attach Magnetic Skins  
![Step 9](tutorials/rtx2080/step9.png)  
Choose and attach a magnetic decal skin to customize the appearance.

---

### Step 10: Power On & Test  
![Step 10](tutorials/rtx2080/step10.png)  
Boot your PC and confirm that the fans and RGB are working. Monitor temps to ensure proper installation.

---

## ✅ Installation Complete  
You’ve successfully installed FANMOD on your RTX 2080 ASUS OC Edition! Enjoy enhanced cooling and custom styling.
